'''Aɛli Fergani''', ilul ass n {{azmez|21|ctamber|1952}} di [[Onnaing]] ([[Fransa]]),  seg twacult [[Tamurt Taqbaylit|taqbaylit]] , d amarir n [[takurt n uḍar|tkurt n uḍar]] aqbur n [[taɣlamt tazzayrit n tkurt n uḍar|agraɣlan]] [[Dzayer|azzayri]] id yuɣalen sakkin d [[asleɣmay]] n [[taɣlamt tazzayrit n tkurt n uḍar|teɣlamt taɣelnawt tazzayrit]].

Yesɛa-d 64 tifrayin deg 64 teɣlamt taɣelnawt gar [[1973 deg takurt n uḍar|1973]] d [[1986 deg takurt n uḍar|1986]].
